WOMAN: (ON SCREEN)
 I was wondering 
 what he was doing...

188
00:07:54,875 --> 00:07:55,876
This way.

189
00:07:58,746 --> 00:08:00,247
-(WHISPERING) Right here.
-Thank you.

190
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:01,715
Mmm-hmm.

191
00:08:01,749 --> 00:08:02,950
Excuse me.

192
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,656
(SOFTLY) Ah, sorry.

193
00:08:08,689 --> 00:08:10,023
I'm so sorry.

194
00:08:11,324 --> 00:08:14,127
Excuse me, excuse me.

195
00:08:14,161 --> 00:08:17,598
WOMAN 2: Now, I never know 
 what my son may be doing. 
(CHUCKLES)

196
00:08:17,631 --> 00:08:19,066
Perhaps it's just as well.

197
00:08:19,099 --> 00:08:20,934
WOMAN 1: Oh, why?

198
00:08:20,968 --> 00:08:22,603
WOMAN 2: Have a look 
 at those eyes, my dear,

199
00:08:22,636 --> 00:08:24,271
perhaps you'll understand 
 what I mean.

200
00:08:26,774 --> 00:08:27,975
He's very handsome. 
 (CHUCKLES)

